{"tid":2394687,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"一人N個自以為好冷嘅古代至近代冷知識","createTime":"2021-02-04T10:46:37.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-04T12:50:48.000Z","uid":90457,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"2bf16c738a93178a1444cb586ca490c1b529f555","tid":2394687,"uid":90457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-04T10:46:37.000Z","msg":"東斯拉夫第一邦國基輔羅斯係由作為「東歐維京人」華蘭茲人（Varangian）其中一個首領留里克嘅繼承者所建立<br />\n<br />\n即使被拜占庭帝國招安為羅馬軍隊成員，華蘭茲人專屬嘅隊伍都係好大陣北歐味<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/KZUseDS.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKZUseDS.jpg&h=c4eb5967&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n而後東斯拉夫文化圈譬如莫斯科等等諾夫哥羅德體系邦國嘅貴族(Druzhina、Boyar)上到戰場大概都係噉嘅裝束（少少脫離現實），偏好使用鈍器、單手斧、北歐式嘅劍，而唔係中世紀晚期東歐流行嘅馬刀<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Qd4LLNZ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQd4LLNZ.jpg&h=bcbd781d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zXVCBWL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzXVCBWL.jpg&h=50cd9598&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n烏克蘭嘅國徽大概可以追溯到留里克王朝通用嘅紋章圖案<br />\n<br />\nAD980<br />\n「偉大的」波羅茲米( Volodymyr the great )時代其中一枚錢幣<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Dhoc96V.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDhoc96V.png&h=edb224b4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nAD1019<br />\n「聰明人」也羅斯拉夫( Yaroslav the wise ) 時代其中一枚錢幣<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jF0bGhU.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjF0bGhU.png&h=f12b7c38&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"fc4a7675919d838a1de430c4d02f55d9e2bd4ce0","tid":2394687,"uid":218158,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-04T11:08:36.000Z","msg":"留名"},{"pid":"0f2b1eda8f81f15b4a401481d3f8ad0b34dd05be","tid":2394687,"uid":371849,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-04T11:10:30.000Z","msg":"伊斯蘭教嘅阿拉就係天主教嘅上帝，算唔算？"},{"pid":"c276fc4017698f835b6854a866bc4a062281d4b5","tid":